### REST Client for Node.js TypeScript App

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrlHttps = https://localhost:3443

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Welcome Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Test POST Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "message": "This is a test message",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-23"
}

### HTTPS Health Check (requires certificate)
GET {{baseUrlHttps}}/health

### HTTPS POST Request (requires certificate)
POST {{baseUrlHttps}}/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "HTTPS Test",
  "message": "This is an HTTPS test message",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-23"
}
